---
const stats = [
  { number: '+50', label: 'Eventos' },
  { number: '+30', label: 'Marcas' },
  { number: '+5', label: 'Anos de experiencia' },
  { number: '+100', label: 'Colaboraciones' },
];
---

<section id="sobre-mi" class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-72 h-72 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-72 h-72 bg-secondary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Title -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-up">
      <p class="text-primary font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-3">Conoceme</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-dark">
        Sobre <span class="gradient-text">Mi</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Photo -->
      <div class="slide-left">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Main image placeholder -->
          <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-[3/4] bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 via-purple/20 to-secondary/20">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-20 h-20 text-primary/40 mx-auto mb-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
                <p class="text-dark/40 text-sm">Foto de Stephanny</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Decorative border -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full rounded-2xl border-2 border-primary/30 -z-10"></div>
          <!-- Floating accent -->
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center animate-float shadow-lg">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">SC</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="slide-right">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-dark mb-6">
          Una apasionada por conectar marcas con personas
        </h3>
        <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Soy Stephanny Cabas, asesora comercial, promotora y modelo profesional con mas de 5 anos de
          experiencia en el mundo del marketing, eventos y moda. Mi pasion es ayudar a las marcas a
          destacar y conectar genuinamente con su audiencia.
        </p>
        <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          He tenido el privilegio de trabajar con diversas marcas reconocidas, participando en campanas
          publicitarias, eventos corporativos y sesiones fotograficas. Cada proyecto es una oportunidad
          para crear algo unico y memorable.
        </p>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 stagger-children">
          {stats.map((stat) => (
            <div class="scale-in text-center p-4 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors duration-300">
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text mb-1">{stat.number}</p>
              <p class="text-dark/60 text-sm">{stat.label}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
